summary:
Internationally oriented marketing and communication professional with extensive experience in multinational FMCG environment, as an independent entrepreneur and lecturer. A true believer and a devoted promotor of internationalisation of higher education.

Proven track record in successful brand building through deep consumer understanding on such brands as: Smirnoff Ice, Baileys, Schwarzkopf Poly Color and others.

Extensive international experience: worked for more than 20 years in The Netherlands and 4 years in Poland, lived and studied for 2 years in France. 

Specialties:
-Marketing and brand strategy development;
-Brand positioning;
-Launch and re-launch strategies development and execution;
-Market and consumer research analysis;
-Measurement and evaluation of marketing programs.
